"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1547861fa1ce5d6da4a5f61d57cb12fdc66d1e9","tid":866666,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"佢係三毛 咁成龍呢"},{"pid":"8ddf76cf09b41ee23ebec371c3788cfce38dc6c6","tid":866666,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"港產片死因太過老套, 同港劇一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9493f3d090cd45e4997b778b8c7a566f82f5e4","tid":866666,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"劇本係個foundation臨時執就話啫<br />\n無戲本就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99b1531ac6cbe6208961b9c731afd1f51227391","tid":866666,"uid":140302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"唔講錢同政治住，根本香港好多行業都係好多老屎忽喺度阻撚住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2ca3d4b9276eb645929a017f959fdfad13b0cd","tid":866666,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0629899d43e20654280d8311451986e96e92ee6d","tid":866666,"uid":11148,"like":160,"dislike":1,"score":159,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"就算政府幫你2,000萬，啲人唔係正正經經利用呢2,000萬將香港電影市道再帶番起，而係諗搵你1,800萬、袋咗落個袋先。好多人都有呢啲咁嘅私心<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係華人賤種最卑劣低賤既地方,科學園搞唔起都係呢個原因<br />\n<br />\n冇計下賤民族係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"咁都可以spin到唔關政府事<br />\n香港電影第一日開始就係洗黑錢工具<br />\n呢個都關産業性質事，拍戲開支複雜容易作大<br />\n<br />\n但係一樣造就左香港嘅軟實力<br />\n真正收皮係2003年簽左CEPA<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>從某天起，中國香港簽咗啲嘢，自此香港電影分為「合拍片」、「純港片」。<br />\n<br />\n你見那些混雜大陸演員的港産片，稱為合拍片。<br />\n<br />\n「合拍片」相對「純港片」的最大分別，就是符合了一堆條件後，可以在大陸大量上映，票房相對「純港片」多數十倍。但既然在大量規則、審批底下，合拍片的創作難度便大大提升，好易變「垃圾」。<br />\n<br />\n「點解唔爭氣呀？點解唔拍返純港片呀？」這就落入了一個惡性循環的局面。票房少，成本自然少。而成本少，所影響的質素差距絕對比你想像更大。本地觀眾又繼續嫌棄的話，票房就少之又少之又少。我又怎能夠投資幾千萬落一套港人都不撐的純港片？好多人都不是想賺人仔，只是港幣賺不得而已。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本政治就係最大因素，冇人可以獨善其身"},{"pid":"a07ba3e500c2519759e20f659fd1e8800e5004ec","tid":866666,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb0880c5c0e985d32cc62ec228a9fd13e31dcea8","tid":866666,"uid":167658,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">恬妞指因無劇本只得大綱，第一日拍戲會緊張</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2019年都黎，仲玩飛紙仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以好睇得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T14:05:41.000Z","msg":"老屎忽:我有經驗，識執生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878a30521d8ab0ce9909802cd3806c30b8d27d81","tid":866666,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T14:06:38.000Z","msg":"自己知自己事啦<br />\n自甘墜落就係咁"},{"pid":"9a82dffd5af0a96c8cce7083feca2597e6172cc6","tid":866666,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f99b1531ac6cbe6208961b9c731afd1f51227391","tid":866666,"uid":140302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"唔講錢同政治住，根本香港好多行業都係好多老屎忽喺度阻撚住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T14:10:06.000Z","msg":"點會唔關政治事<br />\n你有民主，咪可以去參選，去助選<br />\n夠議席咪立法阻止壟斷"},{"pid":"d43bd0c32fac5da0796840afcc5572a1cc46d9d3","tid":866666,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8dc4753e8567c2611fce8f92e5b215e44ea72996","tid":866666,"uid":57848,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"電影不嬲係貼地，反映現實，再扭下橋，到肉先至好睇。唔使宣傳正能量，唔使大製作，就係現實殘酷，電影應該更殘酷。<br />\n<br />\n戰狼果啲之所以紅，係中國人鐘意打飛機，中國人都冇悲劇，亦冇悲劇精神，你套嘢出到國咪畀人笑，唔識反省只識自high嘅民族配上一部一地精嘅電影，絕配。<br />\n<br />\n香港地仲有電影，一套十年，影響人地其他國家都拍十年，點會冇電影？成日武打咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"好中好到肉"},{"pid":"8043eae14f49b6db4a41a21bdf70e1a737c5a13f","tid":866666,"uid":26773,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T15:10:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">恬妞</span></strong>指因無劇本只得大綱，第一日拍戲會緊張，不過第二日已進入狀態，但佢最想嘅其實係開演唱會：「希望3年內可以喺紅館開演唱會，做戲幾廿年想突破，我唔係咁鍾意做戲，我鍾意唱歌，享受燈光音響同掌聲。」記者提議<span style=\"color: red;\">搵林敏驄填詞，她非常驚訝，唔信對方有音樂造詣。</span><br />\n<br />\n邊撚個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b947e55293e11518f82263c3c6220e0fd2a4bf","tid":866666,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e9493f3d090cd45e4997b778b8c7a566f82f5e4","tid":866666,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"劇本係個foundation臨時執就話啫<br />\n無戲本就真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"等睇成套戲啲廢話多過對白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315ece54cced49dfe918269f5ec65978f8bcecd7","tid":866666,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d2d69b90e6fa84701298f14631fd71d41554a732","tid":866666,"uid":167658,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2374eada6d0297086a93b2a441ffb605f1243ba8","tid":866666,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cb0880c5c0e985d32cc62ec228a9fd13e31dcea8","tid":866666,"uid":167658,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T11:57:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">恬妞指因無劇本只得大綱，第一日拍戲會緊張</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2019年都黎，仲玩飛紙仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以好睇得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T12:08:17.000Z","msg":"唔少MARVEL戲都係飛紙仔<br />\n<br />\n如IRON MAN頭兩集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"Hollywood拍戲㸃冇劇本呀<br />\nRDJ即興加減對白就有可能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://mentalfloss.com/article/59310/8-movies-started-shooting-without-completed-script\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmentalfloss.com%2Farticle%2F59310%2F8-movies-started-shooting-without-completed-script&d=MhuHPZVxdG7nVaFusxlDhIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=944aa20f\" target=\"_blank\">http://mentalfloss.com/article/59310/8-movies-started-shooting-without-completed-script</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIron Man<br />\n<br />\nAccording to star Jeff Bridges, Iron Man&mdash;the first movie in the Marvel Cinematic Universe&mdash;went into production with just an outline when the studio rushed production in March 2007 to make the movie's May 2008 release date. &quot;They had no script, man. They had an outline,&quot; the actor, who played Obadiah Stane (a.k.a. Iron Monger) told io9. &quot;We would show up for big scenes every day and we wouldn't know what we were going to say. We would have to go into our trailer and work on this scene and call up writers on the phone, 'You got any ideas?' Meanwhile the crew is tapping their foot on the stage waiting for us to come on. You would think with a $200 million movie you'd have the sh*t together, but it was just the opposite. And the reason for that is because they get ahead of themselves. They have a release date before the script.&quot;"},{"pid":"7045875480f115c23db290c6db4aa03c3cef2f38","tid":866666,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e9493f3d090cd45e4997b778b8c7a566f82f5e4","tid":866666,"uid":75156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"劇本係個foundation臨時執就話啫<br />\n無戲本就真係<img src=\"/assets/